      "rationale": "Systematic mesh refinement study conducted on the pedicle screw–rod construct geometry. Production mesh (≈ 320 000 elements, second-order tetrahedral) yields GCI of 1.8% for stiffness, 2.1% for yield force, and 2.7% for force at 40 mm. All below 3% threshold; required level 3 achieved."
    },
