      "rationale": "An independent FDA biomedical engineer reviewed the Ansys model setup, material assignments, contact definitions, and post-processing macros. Four minor discrepancies identified and corrected prior to production runs. Review documented in project record PR-2023-0047. Required level 2 achieved."
