      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from certified material test reports for production Ti-6Al-4V bar stock. Geometric inputs from CMM measurements of production hardware with stated uncertainty. Input uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo (n = 1000).",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus and Poisson ratio from certified material test reports (lot-specific). Screw and rod geometry from CMM measurements (uncertainty ± 0.01 mm). Monte Carlo propagation (n = 1000) yields combined input uncertainty uinput < 3% on all QoIs, well within acceptance bounds. Required level 3 achieved."
    },
    {
