      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA boundary conditions and material inputs demonstrably equivalent to experimental conditions; any deviations quantified and their effect on QoIs bounded.",
      "rationale": "Experimental boundary conditions (fixture geometry, applied displacement, constraint) replicated in FEA. Polyethylene block compliance measured experimentally and incorporated into FEA model as a spring element (k = 1420 N/mm). Deviation in block stiffness representation bounded to < 1.5% QoI effect via sensitivity study. Required level 3 achieved."
