      "rationale": "E/uval computed per ASME V&V 40 Eq. 5.1 for stiffness (1.31), yield force (1.54), and force at 40 mm (1.78). All values below 1.96 threshold. Validation uncertainty uval computed as RSS of experimental standard deviation, model input uncertainty, and GCI-derived numerical uncertainty. Required level 3 achieved."
